bs-pro-distribution-droplet-embed-desc: Mambu ya nganda ya bo me kotisa na Git, mu mbandu. Bafichi ya bo me tula kidimbu
bs-pro-distribution-droplet-bitbucket-de: Fichier ya bo me kotisa na BitBucket
bs-pro-distribution-droplets-ec-embed-la: Mosi na kati ya [https://prismjs.com/#ndinga ya bo ke pesaka maboko]. Yo kele mfunu kaka kana bo me mona ve ndinga na ndonga ya ba fiche.
bs-pro-distribution-droplets-ec-embed-sh: Songa kaka bandinga ya sikisiki. Yo lenda vanda nimero ya ndonga mosi to ndonga ya kukabwana ti kisono (-). Bo lenda kabula bantalu ya ndonga to bandonga mingi na ba commes.
bs-pro-distribution-ec-config-file-white: Lisiti ya bansangu ya bo me pesa nswa. Bikila yo mpamba sambu yo vanda ve ti ndilu.
bs-pro-distribution-ec-config-domain-whi: Lisiti ya ba domain yina bo me pesa nswa ya kukotisa mambu ya kele na kati. Kukotisa ve protocole, kaka domain. Mu mbandu, Yo kele mbote sambu na yo. Bikila yo mpamba sambu yo vanda ve ti ndilu.
